This example illustrates how to run scMaui to integrated single-cell multiomics datasets with single-omics datasets
using PBMC data from 10X Genomics.
We use a dataset with paired measurements (scRNA + scATAC) and jointly model it with an additional scRNA-seq dataset.

To download and prepare the datasets run:
bash 00_downloads.bash
python 02_prepare_rna_atac_multiome.py
python 03_combine_scrna_rna_multiome.py

To run data integration using only the scRNA-seq portion of the data use:
python 04_run_scmaui_rna_nocorr.py
python 04_run_scmaui_rna_cond.py
python 04_run_scmaui_rna_adv.py

To run data integration using scRNA-seq and scATAC-seq modalities from different batches use:
python 05_run_scmaui_multi_nocorrection.py
python 05_run_scmaui_multi_adversarial.py
